The only fear I have about World of Warcraft is that their playerbase carries over, from games like Starcraft, Warcraft and especially Diablo.<br>
I truely hope that WoW will be a &quot;real&quot; MMORPG like Everquest is, or was supposed to be. Just as long as it doesn't degenerate to a player-vs-player killing fest, then I think I'll be there from release. (From what I gather DAoC is focusing pretty much on player-vs-player, so I hope they dont go down that road with WoW, as well)<br>
Do anyone know if there will be a &quot;roleplaying server&quot; in WoW?<br>
<br>
Not to turn this into a WoW vs EQII thread or anything, but the screenshots I have seen of the EQII player models doesn't really look good, in my opinion. They all look way to human-like, but then again I also really liked the old Troll models better than the new one, so maybe its just my taste that is weird. :o)<br>
